      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "## New Features\r\n\r\n- **Column Visibility Toggle**: You can now customize your view by toggling individual columns on and off within the \"View Options\" menu. Tailor the interface to show only the data you need.\r\n- **Enhanced Popup Menu**: Introduced a new custom context menu providing quick access to essential actions:\r\n    - **Refresh data**: Updates the view with the latest command history.\r\n    - **Reset sorts and filters**: Clears all active sorting and filtering to restore the default view.\r\n    - **Copy as CSV**: Copies the current table data to the clipboard in CSV format.\r\n    - **Export as CSV**: Exports the current table data as a CSV file (Desktop app only).\r\n\r\n## Improvements\r\n\r\n- Minor improvements.\r\n\r\n## Acknowledgments\r\n\r\nA special thank you to [@codey-badger](https://github.com/codey-badger) for the excellent suggestions in [#3](https://github.com/namikaze-40p/obsidian-command-tracker/issues/3#issuecomment-3658869175).\r\nYour feedback helps make this plugin better for everyone!",
